      "contents": "Lemma op_compatible_cons {\u03c3 : Signature} {A : Algebra \u03c3}\n  (\u03a6 : \u2200 s, Relation (A s)) `{!IsCongruence A \u03a6}\n  (s : Sort \u03c3) (w : SymbolType \u03c3) (f : Operation A (s ::: w))\n  (x : A s) (P : OpCompatible A \u03a6 f)\n  : OpCompatible A \u03a6 (f x).",
      "messages": [],
